article_id:288,category_name:Events,title_name:Epilogue Added to the A Waltz with Fate Raid Event ,image_path:,message:<div>An epilogue has been added to the raid event A Waltz with Fate, which ended <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1552370399"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>You can view the epilogue by tapping the banner on the upper-left corner of the Home screen, which can be accessed from the in-game footer menu, then selecting View Quests.</div><div><br></div><div>â– Epilogue Availability</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1552370400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1552975199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>The epilogue can be viewed only by players who have completed up to chapter 5 of the event&rsquo;s story.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1552370400,update_time1552283938